1
00:02:27,080 --> 00:02:28,599
You said you were going to disappear.

2
00:02:28,599 --> 00:02:30,000
Did you mean running away to Shen'ao?

3
00:02:30,960 --> 00:02:31,639
Yeah.

4
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,080
In Hangzhou,

5
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,400
I can run into him anywhere.

6
00:02:35,719 --> 00:02:37,319
I had to disappear for a while.

7
00:02:37,919 --> 00:02:38,319
Did you see
the photos I sent you?

8
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:41,639
Shen'ao is really beautiful.

9
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:43,800
Maybe this trip to gather inspiration

10
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,520
will actually lead to new ideas.

11
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,719
Alright, good luck with your trip.

12
00:02:50,919 --> 00:02:53,039
[I'll wait for your return in Hangzhou.]

13
00:02:56,840 --> 00:02:59,000
[I've already made contact with Mr. Zhang.]

14
00:02:59,280 --> 00:03:01,240
[Please wait for good news.]

15
00:03:09,599 --> 00:03:10,360
Lawyer?

16
00:03:11,039 --> 00:03:11,520
Yes.

17
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,960
