21
00:03:19,599 --> 00:03:20,120
Well,
I'm now

22
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,360
Miss Shen's attorney.

23
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:23,039
If you have any questions,
you can discuss them with me first.

24
00:03:24,159 --> 00:03:25,800
How can I discuss it with you?

25
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:28,080
This is a personal matter between us.

26
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:29,520
Fine.

27
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:31,360
Even if she has appointed you
to handle the lawsuit against me,

28
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:34,240
