to ask for their return.

38
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:46,439
Wait,

39
00:03:46,439 --> 00:03:48,039
I never said I wouldn't marry her.

40
00:03:48,520 --> 00:03:50,439
It's her who insisted on breaking up.

41
00:03:51,039 --> 00:03:51,560
And those gifts
were given willingly.

42
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:54,479
Whether they were given willingly

43
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,560
