47
00:03:59,159 --> 00:04:01,240
It proves that during your relationship,

48
00:04:01,759 --> 00:04:02,599
you used

49
00:04:02,719 --> 00:04:03,719
the excuse that marrying

50
00:04:03,719 --> 00:04:05,479
