61
00:04:23,360 --> 00:04:24,439
Sorry, Mr. Zhang.

62
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:26,720
Even though I'm a man,

63
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,879
I can't agree with

64
00:04:28,879 --> 00:04:29,839
